    "description": "Delsole Corporation manufactures and sells pizza and ethnic bread products in Japan. The company offers pizza crust and dough products; bread products, including naan, focaccia, tortilla, pita, and biscuits; shredded cheese; and cheese fry and naan dog snack products to supermarket chains and various food service companies. It also trades in pizza and basil sauces, and curries; olives and jalapenos; meat and chicken products comprising pepperoni, Italian sausages, taco meat, chicken sticks, chicken drops, and spicy chicken drops. In addition, the company operates restaurants and department store food counters, as well as provides take-out and home delivery services. Delsole Corporation distributes its products under the Del Sole label. The company was formerly known as JC Comsa Corporation. Delsole Corporation was incorporated in 1964 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
